      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the advice. i'm just really anxious about it. i feel like if i go to the er it'll just be a waste of time and money if it's just gas. i really don't want to go to the hospital. the ibuprofen seems okay, but how much can i actually take to make sure the pain stops so i can rest? i have the 400mg ones, is it safe to take like 3 or 4 at once just for tonight?",
