      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that makes me feel a bit better about the dose. the pain is still pretty sharp but it's kind of a dull ache now which i think is normal for cramps. i'm also feeling a bit nauseous but i'm sure it's just from the stress and the pain. i really want to just sleep through the night and see how i feel in the morning. if i take the ibuprofen now, do you think it'll be enough to keep the pain away so i don't have to wake up in the middle of the night? i'm really hoping it's just something minor that i can just deal with at home.",
